1
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,680
The rollout of Market regulation policies

2
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:12,000
will surely curb speculative
property investment.

3
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:16,319
But only by ensuring people's
reasonable housing needs

4
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:18,400
can the real estate market develop steadily.

5
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,560
I've reviewed the bidders' credentials
for this supervision tender.

6
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,200
No issues. Take a look.

7
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:24,680
I trust your judgment.

8
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,040
Good, as long as there's no problem.

9
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,239
The Bidding proceeds as scheduled.

10
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,920
When it's time for the chief supervisor's defense meeting,

11
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,079
I'll go with you.

12
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:37,719
Did you read the government's purchase
and price restriction doc?

13
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:38,560
I saw it.

14
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,760
That document

15
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,079
will heavily impact sales of
Wanhe Mansion Phase 2.

16
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,439
Su Yuanyuan must be under
a lot of pressure too.

17
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,239
We need to talk it over with Zheng,

18
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,200
figure out how to offset
some of her losses.

19
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,560
Oh, my brother from another mother,

20
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,159
always thinking of others.

21
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:57,079
Su Yuanyuan's gonna fall
head over heels for you.

22
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,400
Piss off.

23
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,000
Like I'm not annoyed enough already?

24
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:04,239
Su Yuanyuan's waiting for you at
Wanhe Mansion Phase 2's launch.

25
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,479
Who's going from our company?

26
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,319
Han Lin.

27
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,759
What are you doing here?

28
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,479
I came to take a look.

29
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:54,319
To see how badly you've screwed me over?

30
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,199
Of all times,

31
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:58,879
you waited for Market regulation to sign
the Exclusive Sales Contract.

32
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:01,080
What did I do to you to deserve this?

33
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:02,800
Su Yuanyuan,

34
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:04,159
please calm down first.

35
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:07,520
We didn't know Market regulation
would hit so soon either.

36
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,759
Didn't know?

37
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,479
You didn't hear a single rumor?

38
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,560
Haven't you taken plenty of perks from me?

39
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,680
And you didn't know?

40
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,280
Su Yuanyuan,

41
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,560
I have things to do.

42
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,719
I'll be heading off now.

43
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,680
I'll leave you to it.

44
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:39,400
Su Yuanyuan, a client called in
to complain.

45
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,719
He says the house he bought
was overpriced.

46
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:44,919
Based on the new government policy,

47
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:47,000
he wants to come and return the property.

48
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,520
Is the day he bought it the same as today?

49
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,159
What's your mouth even for?

50
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,240
Can't you explain it yourself?

51
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,719
I did explain.

52
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,000
He won't listen.

53
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,479
He wants to negotiate with you.

54
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,719
Negotiate with me?

55
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,080
Then who do I negotiate with?

56
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,199
You'd better figure out a solution.

57
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,639
Su Yuanyuan,

58
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,280
I...

59
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,120
How am I supposed to solve this?

60
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:04,919
Refund!

61
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,879
Give him a refund!

62
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,800
Refund?

63
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,439
Are you going to cover my losses?

64
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,560
I don't care.

65
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,199
Throw in a balcony, a parking spot,
whatever.

66
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,560
Just keep that client for me.

67
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,599
Su Yuanyuan.

68
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:27,600
Junjie, let's plan Phase 1 as a...

69
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,319
You think tossing this hot potato to me

70
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:42,120
solves everything for you?

71
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,199
Su Yuanyuan,

72
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,480
let's talk this through calmly.

73
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,240
Xiao Yifan, He Junjie,

74
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:51,920
you two owe me an explanation today.

75
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:04,199
The government's Market regulation
on housing prices

76
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:06,399
was something we didn't anticipate either.

77
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,079
And the contract has already been signed.

78
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,160
It's clearly stated in the contract:

79
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,439
losses caused by policy changes

80
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,399
are borne by each side independently.

81
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,040
Su Yuanyuan,

82
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,560
on the Wanhe Mansion Phase 2 project,

83
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,079
we'll find a way

84
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,160
to make up for your losses
as much as possible.

85
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,879
Are you deliberately targeting me?

86
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,639
Is this fun for you?

87
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,680
Why would I target you?

88
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,639
What's in it for me?

89
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,160
Su Yuanyuan,

90
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,920
before we signed the contract,

91
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,480
you were the one breathing down
our necks every day.

92
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,319
When we signed the contract,

93
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:40,879
I asked you if you wanted
more time to think.

94
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:43,079
You were the one who rushed to sign.

95
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,399
But still,

96
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,079
you two can't gang up and
screw me over like this.

97
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:51,720
All my money is tied up in
the Wanhe Mansion project.

98
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,439
We've been friends for over a decade.

99
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:57,319
Are you two just going to watch me
go bankrupt?

100
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,720
We're acting strictly according
to the contract.

101
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,920
Profits and losses are your own concern.

102
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,920
Now that something unexpected has come up,

103
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:07,120
Yifan and I are under huge pressure
negotiating with the company

104
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,920
to make up for your losses.

105
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,920
Yifan,

106
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,000
really?

107
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,439
How are you planning to compensate me?

108
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:20,319
Isn't your husband

109
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,759
in the General Contracting business?

110
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:25,360
Phase 1 of Plot 7's General Contracting
is up for Bidding.

111
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,680
Go back

112
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:29,120
and have Fang Bing prepare
the documents thoroughly.

113
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,759
All else being equal,

114
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,439
you'll get priority.

115
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,720
What?

116
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,759
The Market regulation order
has been issued.

117
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:59,000
Didn't your wife catch
any wind of it?

118
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,040
Monday morning quarterback.

119
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:03,600
The contracts are signed.
Can we take them back?

120
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,319
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

121
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,240
I just found out myself.

122
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:13,480
Xiao Yifan clearly played you.

123
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:18,040
They probably knew Plot 6
was a hot potato.

124
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,199
What they really wanted was Plot 7.

125
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,720
What can we do now?

126
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,959
Grasping at straws.

127
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,319
Sell whatever units we can.

128
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,759
The General Contracting for Plot 7 Phase 1

129
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,519
is about to go up for Bidding.

130
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,639
Do you have a plan?

131
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,079
The person in charge,

132
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,319
is it still Xiao Yifan?

133
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,519
The lead this time

134
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:41,680
is He Junjie.

135
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,399
But let me warn you,

136
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:46,160
He Junjie is just as tough as Xiao Yifan.

137
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:48,199
Even more stubborn, actually.

138
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,480
That's a real headache.

139
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,920
Headache or not, we have to do it.

140
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,839
Plot 7 is the hot commodity now.

141
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,680
We can't screw this up again.

142
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,120
Don't touch me.

143
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,480
I'm not in the mood.

144
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,600
You brought this bad mood on yourself.

145
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:32,879
You've been obsessing over Xiao Yifan.

146
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,480
He dug a pit for you.

147
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,120
And now look at you.

148
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,440
How are you gonna fill it?

149
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,519
How many units did you sell today?

150
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,200
Don't you have any idea?

151
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:43,600
All my earnings went to cover your mess.

152
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:45,639
So what if I touch you?

153
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,200
Who are you to lecture me?

154
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,399
I'm your wife.

155
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:54,399
Spending your money is my right.

156
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,279
Take a good look at yourself.

157
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,879
Without money, would I even be with you?

158
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,159
Have I been too easy on you?

159
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,879
Look at your belly. Any sign of life
all these years?

160
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,639
Xiao Yifan's kid

161
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,679
is already in kindergarten.

162
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,919
You think I actually like you?

163
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,480
If we can make it work, fine.

164
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:14,320
If not, we split.

165
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,039
Fang Bing, you Loser.

166
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,399
The moment I stop making money,
this is the face you show?

167
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,440
Fine, let's split then.

168
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:25,240
With all the dirty things you've done,

169
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,039
you'd be locked up for years.

170
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,519
Let me tell you,

171
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:36,879
if this ever gets out,

172
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,039
I'll kill you.

173
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,919
Bing.

174
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,720
Your hand is so pretty.

175
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,159
Bing.

176
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,679
How did you get hurt?

177
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,679
Does it hurt?

178
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:05,000
Let me blow on it.

179
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,240
Now that you mention it,

180
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,279
it actually does hurt a bit.

181
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:10,279
My wife's nails are too long.

182
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,799
How could she do that?

183
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:16,159
Didn't she just launch and make money?

184
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,519
Made money and still hits you?

185
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,320
She doesn't care, but I do.

186
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,799
What money? I'm the one
covering her losses.

187
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,919
Bing.

188
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,759
I've been feeling strange lately.

189
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:28,279
My period hasn't come either.

190
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,559
Could I be pregnant?

191
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,039
Are you serious?

192
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,519
Boy or girl?

193
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,879
A son, of course.

194
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:40,200
When will you give
our son a home?

195
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,600
Divorce isn't that easy.

196
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,919
You know that too.

197
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:48,039
She and I still have a lot of
business ties.

198
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,840
Bing.

199
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,799
I'm not after anything from you.

200
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,759
Just want you to treat us well.

201
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:02,080
Fine, I'll transfer you
some money tomorrow.

202
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,399
No, if you transfer it,

203
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:07,639
she'll check the accounts
during the divorce.

204
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,879
I'll bring you cash.

205
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,200
And this house,

206
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:13,600
it was also paid by transfer.

207
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,480
Tomorrow I'll have someone buy you one.

208
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,360
You're so good to me.
